            f" 🎯 <b>Daily Goal:</b> {prog_daily} <b>{goal_pct_daily}%</b>\n"
            f"╠{'═'*38}╣\n"
            f"✨ <b>MONTHLY PERFORMANCE</b> ✨\n"
            f" 📈 <b>P/L Mois:</b> <code>{self.stats['profit_month']:.2f} USD</code>\n"
            f" 🎯 <b>Monthly Goal:</b> {prog_monthly} <b>{goal_pct_monthly}%</b>\n"
            f"╠{'═'*38}╣\n"
            f"🚀 <b>LIVE TRADING INFO</b> 🚀\n"
            f" 📡 <b>MT5:</b> <code>{mt_st}</code> | 🧠 <b>AI:</b> <code>{ai_st}</code> | ⚙️ <b>ENGINE:</b> <code>{engine_st}</code>\n"
            f" ⚙️ <b>Trading Active:</b> <code>{'Oui' if state['is_trading'] else 'Non'}</code>\n"
            f" 📊 <b>Lot Actuel:</b> <code>{self.current_lot:.2f}</code>\n"
            f" 🌟 <b>Actif en cours:</b> <code>{self.ai_intel['active_asset']}</code>\n"
            f" 🔄 <b>Trades en cours:</b> <code>(Non implémenté)</code>\n"
